Germany’s Hahn Calls for British Exit From EU, Bild Reports

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-12-11T16:38:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-11/germany-s-hahn-calls-for-british-exit-from-eu-bild-reports.html
The U.K. should leave the European
Union if it refuses to back last week’s rescue pact,  Bild 
newspaper quoted Joerg-Uwe Hahn, minister of European affairs
for the German state of Hesse, as saying in an interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
